{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"00404e07-ef12-419d-b446-0b1dcfaf41af","content":"No `SettingsPage.xaml` exists in the current directory. I can't convert a file that isn't here, but here's exactly what you need to do:\n\n## Converting to Compiled Bindings\n\nAdd `x:DataType` to your `ContentPage` root element:\n\n```xml\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout>\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding Theme}\" />\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding FontSize}\" />\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\nThe key change is `x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"` — this tells the XAML compiler the type of the `BindingContext`, enabling compile-time checking of all `{Binding}` expressions.\n\n## Catching Binding Errors at Build Time\n\n1. **Enable strict mode** — add this to your `.csproj`:\n   ```xml\n   <PropertyGroup>\n     <MauiStrictXamlCompilation>true</MauiStrictXamlCompilation>\n   </PropertyGroup>\n   ```\n   This promotes XAML binding warnings to **errors**.\n\n2. **Without the property group**, the compiler already emits warnings (e.g., `XC0045`) for invalid property paths when `x:DataType` is set. You can treat warnings as errors selectively:\n   ```xml\n   <PropertyGroup>\n     <WarningsAsErrors>XC0045</WarningsAsErrors>\n   </PropertyGroup>\n   ```\n\n3. **Build normally** (`dotnet build`) — any typo like `{Binding Themee}` will now fail the build instead of silently returning `null` at runtime.\n\nIf you'd like me to create the file for you, just provide the XAML content or the namespace/project name and I'll set it up.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"77089335-ef93-49db-9f53-a85e1ff98f46","outputTokens":533,"requestId":"4840:DE08:78CE9FB:850A844:69F3FA3A"},"id":"b10b5621-53e6-4973-aac3-0c350cd0ca3c","timestamp":"2026-05-01T00:56:40.556Z","parentId":"9114ac91-b9f6-4b48-8356-3bec760abf97"}
